Zoro enthuses traditional Hip-Hop beats in his latest audio, “Mbada”, this comes through shortly after his previously released record which celebrates the beauty of an African homely girl titled “OYOKO” (Beautiful homely girl) which features Chidinma. Staying true to his artistry, Zoro delivers with impressive lyrics and flow for his latest banger! No doubt, the rapper goes a notch higher on this one keeping his fans abreast with his finesse and his abilities to flow effortlessly with the Igbo language. Enjoy below as you stand a chance to get on Zoro – Mbada (Remix) Follow Instructions below; Download Mbada instrumental. Make a video/ 1-minute verse, it can be a freestyle or written rap. Tag @zoroswagabag with hashtag #zorombadacover. And three rappers with the best verses will be up in the remix.  Note: There is a file embedded within this post, please visit this post to download the file. The post Stand a Chance to Feature on Zoro’s Mbada Remix appeared first on 360Nobs.com. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from 360Nobs.com. Click here to read the full text on the original website.